# Solar System Card — Design

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph browser["Browser — card.js Tier 1, no sidecar"]
        CARD[card.js<br/>CARD_SHIM global<br/>mica injected]
        CARD -->|creates| SCENE[Three.js Scene]
        CARD -->|creates| RENDERER[WebGL Renderer<br/>antialias + alpha]
        CARD -->|creates| CAMERA[Perspective Camera<br/>FOV 60 degrees]
        CARD -->|controls| CTRL[OrbitControls<br/>zoom / pan / rotate]
        SCENE -->|contains| SUN[Sun mesh<br/>emissive glow]
        SCENE -->|contains| PLANETS[8 Planet meshes<br/>MeshStandardMaterial]
        SCENE -->|contains| RINGS[Saturn RingGeometry<br/>ring texture]
        SCENE -->|contains| ORBITS[Orbital path lines<br/>THREE.Line dashed]
        SCENE -->|contains| STARS[Starfield<br/>THREE.Points]
        SCENE -->|contains| LABELS[Planet name labels<br/>HTML overlay]
        CARD -->|manages| ANIM[Animation loop<br/>requestAnimationFrame]
        ANIM -->|updates| ORBITAL[Orbital positions<br/>Kepler third law]
        ANIM -->|updates| ROTATION[Axial rotation]
        CARD -->|drives| INFO[Info panel<br/>DOM overlay]
        CARD -->|loads via| TEX[THREE.TextureLoader<br/>NASA / Wikimedia URLs]
        TEX -->|fallback| COLOR[Procedural color sphere]
        CARD -->|disposes via| DESTROY[onDestroy hook]
    end

    subgraph external["External resources"]
        CDN[Three.js 0.160.0 UMD<br/>cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm]
        CTRL_ESM[OrbitControls ESM<br/>dynamic import]
        TEX_NASA[NASA / Wikimedia<br/>public-domain textures]
    end

    CDN -->|metadata.scripts| CARD
    CTRL_ESM -->|dynamic import| CARD
    TEX_NASA -->|TextureLoader URLs| TEX
```

